# ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  CODEOWNERS — Earth Love United
# ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
#  Maps file patterns to required reviewers. GitHub enforces this
#  automatically: any PR touching a pattern below cannot merge
#  without an approval from a listed owner.
#
#  Owners are TEAMS, not individuals, so review is not bottlenecked
#  on any one person:
#    @earth-love-united/architects   — code architecture & core systems
#    @earth-love-united/maintainers  — governance, legal, CI, enforcement
#    @earth-love-united/reviewers    — general review pool (repo-wide)
#
#  Teams are created by tools/org-setup.sh. Roles, not agent names,
#  govern review decisions. See AGENTS.md § Operations.
# ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ─── Legal & governance (require maintainer review) ─────────────
/LICENSE                              @earth-love-united/maintainers
/CREDITS.md                           @earth-love-united/maintainers
/CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md                   @earth-love-united/maintainers
/CONTRIBUTING.md                      @earth-love-united/maintainers
/README.md                            @earth-love-united/maintainers

# ─── Architectural authorities (require architect review) ───────
/AGENTS.md                            @earth-love-united/architects
/ARCHITECTURE.md                      @earth-love-united/architects
/SWARM_SDK.md                         @earth-love-united/architects
/OPERATIONS.md                        @earth-love-united/architects

# ─── Core safety layer (the foundation modules) ─────────────────
/js/gaia-utils.js                     @earth-love-united/architects
/js/module-contracts.js               @earth-love-united/architects
/js/module-validator.js               @earth-love-united/architects
/js/app.js                            @earth-love-united/architects

# ─── Cross-module communication & persistence ───────────────────
/js/event-bus.js                      @earth-love-united/architects
/js/storage-adapter.js                @earth-love-united/architects

# ─── Parallel subsystem (ES6 class pattern) ─────────────────────
/js/modules/                          @earth-love-united/architects

# ─── Out-of-band agent↔browser bridge ──────────────────────────
/infra/                               @earth-love-united/architects

# ─── Enforcement scripts (changing these changes the rules) ─────
/scripts/verify_load_order.py         @earth-love-united/maintainers
/tools/agent-precommit                @earth-love-united/maintainers
/tools/install-hooks.sh               @earth-love-united/maintainers
/tools/start-mission.sh               @earth-love-united/maintainers
/tools/end-mission.sh                 @earth-love-united/maintainers
/tools/org-setup.sh                   @earth-love-united/maintainers
/tools/fetch-globe-vendor.sh          @earth-love-united/maintainers
/tools/check-globe-vendor-integrity.js @earth-love-united/maintainers
/tools/lib/globe-vendor-integrity.js  @earth-love-united/maintainers
/tools/fixtures/globe-vendor-integrity.json @earth-love-united/maintainers

# ─── CI / GitHub config ─────────────────────────────────────────
/.github/                             @earth-love-united/maintainers
/.gitignore                           @earth-love-united/maintainers

# ─── Everything else: no required owner ─────────────────────────
# (PRs touching only non-protected paths can auto-merge when CI is green
#  and the auto-merge label is present — see .github/workflows/auto-merge.yml)
